                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">Born in Lincoln, England, in 1815, Boole was a self-taught genius. He came from a humble background and received no formal university education, yet his passion for mathematics was so profound he taught himself multiple languages and advanced calculus.</p>
                <img src="https://placehold.co/400x300/e5e7eb/4b5563?text=Lincoln%2C%20England" alt="Image of Lincoln, England" class="mt-8 mx-auto rounded-xl shadow-lg">
