        <!-- Slide 4: Contribution to AI -->
        <div id="slide-3" class="slide-container">
            <div class="slide-content">
                <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold">The Foundation of AI</h2>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">While Boole's work predates modern AI, it is its conceptual bedrock. Every single decision, calculation, and piece of data in an AI model—from a simple chatbot to a complex neural network—is processed as binary code (1s and 0s). Boole's system provided the mathematical framework for this binary logic.</p>
                <img src="https://placehold.co/400x300/e5e7eb/4b5563?text=Digital%20Circuitry" alt="Diagram of a logic circuit" class="mt-8 mx-auto rounded-xl shadow-lg">
