                <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold">An Enduring Legacy</h2>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">Boole's work is the reason we can automate complex logical tasks. His genius transformed logic from a philosophical concept into a practical mathematical tool. He is rightly considered the "Father of the Digital Age" and a foundational pioneer of artificial intelligence.</p>
                <img src="https://placehold.co/400x300/e5e7eb/4b5563?text=Boole%27s%20Legacy" alt="Image representing technological progress" class="mt-8 mx-auto rounded-xl shadow-lg">
